{"tid":311390,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"女兒李嫣參加catwalk，腿長氣質超似王菲！","createTime":"2017-07-06T14:40:57.000Z","updateTime":"2017-07-07T09:02:25.000Z","uid":58099,"like":1,"dislike":30,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"4d19a0fc184473cb2df85831a6f63fb74849d1a0","tid":311390,"uid":58099,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-06T14:40:57.000Z","msg":"法國童裝品牌Bonpoint於法國時間5號喺巴黎舉行童裝2018春夏騷，話明係童裝，當然係由小朋友行騷。成班外國小朋友裡面，有兩個華人小朋友，其中一個係11歲李嫣，即係王菲細女。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n上月30號，李嫣小朋友已經成身Bonpoint，由李亞鵬陪住，喺北京機場現身，着上短袖鬆身嘅娃娃裙，以粉色配綠色拼色設計，似乎「童話小公主」，再加上佢遺傳咗媽咪王菲嘅長腿，相當清純!<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/07/06/223816_9913dde48be7d443935378195d2f95d9.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F07%2F06%2F223816_9913dde48be7d443935378195d2f95d9.jpg&h=be023c6e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/07/06/223816_af493273fb7197e5d6908f97cd8b90e8.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F07%2F06%2F223816_af493273fb7197e5d6908f97cd8b90e8.jpg&h=dd81b924&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n而李嫣行騷時，佢亦好淡定咁似足「國際名模」，擺出高冷嘅表情，面上散發出自信，爸爸李亞鵬就喺台下望住愛女首次行騷，李嫣一共有兩個造型，一套係金屬粉色連身裙配小白鞋，另一套藍色連衣裙配花環。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/07/06/223850_f969d3bec147103aef8901629ec368d9.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F07%2F06%2F223850_f969d3bec147103aef8901629ec368d9.jpg&h=04004045&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n李嫣接受媒體訪問時，話自己鍾意同朋友行街，佢着衫都有自己風格，一向喜歡襯衫，稱褲同裙要睇場合去着，講起王菲着衫行簡約風格，不過有唔少名牌衫，李嫣霸氣咁答：「從來沒偷穿過媽媽的高跟鞋，雖然媽媽的衣服多，比我的多，但我的衣服（本身）就很好看了。」問到佢將來想做啲咩，李嫣就話未諗到，會唔會演戲同唱歌都唔知道，李嫣相當乖巧，回答認真，講話有自信。"},{"pid":"4648eed2061c0f932f1dcb2b976bc160853a74ac","tid":311390,"uid":58099,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-06T14:48:03.000Z","msg":","},{"pid":"34e9ba6ce5730c282f681df146df504024911841","tid":311390,"uid":71303,"like":17,"dislike":0,"score":17,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-06T14:50:01.000Z","msg":"睇錯李偲嫣"},{"pid":"ef8a106579f38f09fb32cef59636c094fed47ac5","tid":311390,"uid":12573,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-06T14:50:21.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>睇錯李偲嫣</blockquote><br />\n我都係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8ff628024364e11f4263322a8f2ffc06e4490349","tid":311390,"uid":21480,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-06T14:50:27.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"6a712beeb9ffa65a860cb52149d4f17ab0240c23","tid":311390,"uid":127100,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-06T14:51:48.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>睇錯李偲嫣</blockquote><br />\n <br />\n我都係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3f934518f911a0afbc6bdd42c5af0ffafcbf6036","tid":311390,"uid":8957,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-06T16:42:56.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>有啲似生極都係女嗰條友<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\nx2<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b1de2b2067a80974faebc25632f52961cc4016e0","tid":311390,"uid":58099,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-06T16:44:48.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>有啲似生極都係女嗰條友<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n氣質滿滿"},{"pid":"a31d024341506bac1e782df3ab40bd48439ada0f","tid":311390,"uid":48124,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-06T17:24:43.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>睇錯李偲嫣</blockquote><br />\n <br />\n我都係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\nsame<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e6dafaa67303e2f66b86ec25185356